              <DefinitionShort>to change one’s manner of life in a particular direction, with the implication of turning back to God</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to change one’s ways</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to turn to God</Gloss>
                <Gloss>repentance</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
